               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 2ra-28va)
 I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 2ra-5rb)
 I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 5rb-8rb)
 I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... "I worship Thee ..." (fol. 8va-9va)
 I-4) Taʾammǝra Māryām
                     "Miracles of Mary": 20 miracles (fols. 9va-28va)
 II) Excerpt from a
                     lectionary (fols. 29ra-36vb)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-2 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Māryām ʾǝmmu la-ʾIyasus Krǝstos kahāli ...
                        "O my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of Jesus Christ the Almighty ..."
                           (<locus target="#7rb">7rb-</locus>va) (cp. ChRep n<locus target="#373">373</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- salām laki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Māryām ʾǝmma madḫǝn wa-ʾǝmma
                        bǝrhān ... "Salutation to you, o my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of the
                        Saviour and Mother of the Light ..."(<locus from="7va" to="8rb">7va-8rb</locus>).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The miracles of Text I-4 are not numbered.</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The arrangement of Text II is similar to the scriptural readings for the
                        days of the week, cp. Ms. S<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>(Maṣḥafa gǝṣṣǝw) for</note>
                     <note>- Sunday: <locus from="29ra" to="31vb">29ra-31vb</locus> (S<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>: <locus from="54vb" to="59ra">54vb-59ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- Friday: <locus from="31vb" to="34rb">31vb-34rb</locus> (S<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>: <locus from="50rb" to="52ra">50rb-52ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- Saturday: <locus from="34rb" to="36vb">34rb-36vb</locus> (S<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>: <locus from="52ra" to="54vb">52ra-54vb</locus>).</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
